[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":367},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fpython\u002F20190531\u002F4077454772\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fpython\u002F20190531\u002F4077454772\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fpython\u002F20190531\u002F4077454772\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fpython\u002F20190531\u002F4077454772\u002F":344,"related:\u002Fpython\u002F20190531\u002F4077454772\u002F":353},"\u002Fen\u002Fpython\u002F2019\u002F05\u002F31\u002Fauto-generate-video-subtitles-with-python\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":67,"date":328,"description":18,"extension":329,"lang":330,"meta":331,"navigation":332,"path":333,"readingMinutes":334,"seo":335,"standalone":336,"stem":337,"tags":338,"tldr":341,"updated":341,"url":342,"__hash__":343},"content\u002FPython\u002F使用-Python-替影片自動產生字幕-srt-檔.md","使用 Python 替影片自動產生字幕 srt 檔","4077454772",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":319},"minimark",[11,15,19,22,25,28,56,59,62,69,72,89,92,98,101,110,113,116,125,131,134,143,149,164,171,174,180,183,188,192,198,208,214,217,223,227,230,239,245,248,253,256,265,268,277,280,289,292,298,301,308,315],[12,13,14],"h2",{"id":14},"前言",[16,17,18],"p",{},"有時候我們要替影片上字幕是滿麻煩的事情，因為必須重複地聽才能夠抓出時間區段，但是如果透過工具先幫我們抓出 50% 字幕區間，然後在來做調整，這樣一定會比較準確，所以這邊做一下筆記該如何使用這個套件。",[16,20,21],{},"※ 注意這是透過 Google Translate 替我們抓出語音辨識的，所以可能翻譯出來會有點好笑(?)，所以翻譯出來的結果主要也是與主講人口齒清晰度有關係。",[12,23,24],{"id":24},"使用工具",[16,26,27],{},"由於在 Window 上使用會稍微複雜一點，主要會使用到這幾個東西",[29,30,31,42,49],"ul",{},[32,33,34,35],"li",{},"Python 2.7.12 ",[36,37,41],"a",{"href":38,"rel":39},"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.python.org\u002Fftp\u002Fpython\u002F2.7.12\u002Fpython-2.7.12.msi",[40],"nofollow","Download",[32,43,44,45],{},"ffmpeg ",[36,46,41],{"href":47,"rel":48},"https:\u002F\u002Fsourceforge.net\u002Fprojects\u002Fffmpegwindowsbi\u002Ffiles\u002F?source=navbar",[40],[32,50,51,52],{},"autosub ",[36,53,41],{"href":54,"rel":55},"https:\u002F\u002Fgithub.com\u002Fagermanidis\u002Fautosub\u002Ffiles\u002F1177869\u002Fautosub_app.0.3.12.zip",[40],[12,57,58],{"id":58},"流程操作",[16,60,61],{},"1.安裝 Python 2.7.12 (我已經安裝過了，所以就直接忽略吧)",[16,63,64],{},[65,66],"img",{"alt":67,"src":68},"Python","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FmmcIY0m.png",[16,70,71],{},"2.開啟命令字元視窗 (CMD) 輸入以下指令\n我是習慣使用 PowerShell。",[73,74,79],"pre",{"className":75,"code":76,"language":77,"meta":78,"style":78},"language-cmd shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","C:\\Python27\\Scripts\\pip.exe install autosub\n","cmd","",[80,81,82],"code",{"__ignoreMap":78},[83,84,87],"span",{"class":85,"line":86},"line",1,[83,88,76],{},[16,90,91],{},"安裝過程會稍微有點久，所以輸入完之後可以泡一下茶...",[16,93,94],{},[65,95],{"alt":96,"src":97},"Image","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002F2ElD6PH.png",[16,99,100],{},"如果不想用上面這種方式也可以用另一種安裝指令，基本上大同小異",[73,102,104],{"className":75,"code":103,"language":77,"meta":78,"style":78},"C:\\Python27\\Scripts\\pip.exe install https:\u002F\u002Fpypi.python.org\u002Fpackages\u002F35\u002F7b\u002F9d5361c0f7abfcc6d826a5279b1c4501f7616505629f6c54857587ec6e37\u002Fautosub-0.3.9.tar.gz\n",[80,105,106],{"__ignoreMap":78},[83,107,108],{"class":85,"line":86},[83,109,103],{},[16,111,112],{},"3.安裝完畢後，要輸入以下指令更改剛剛安裝的套件檔名(很重要)",[16,114,115],{},"CMD 作法:",[73,117,119],{"className":75,"code":118,"language":77,"meta":78,"style":78},"Rename C:\\Python27\\Scripts\\autosub autosub_app.py\n",[80,120,121],{"__ignoreMap":78},[83,122,123],{"class":85,"line":86},[83,124,118],{},[16,126,127],{},[65,128],{"alt":129,"src":130},"CMD","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FdSLs4J5.png",[16,132,133],{},"Powershell 做法:",[73,135,137],{"className":75,"code":136,"language":77,"meta":78,"style":78},"Rename-Item C:\\Python27\\Scripts\\autosub.py autosub_app.py\n",[80,138,139],{"__ignoreMap":78},[83,140,141],{"class":85,"line":86},[83,142,136],{},[16,144,145],{},[65,146],{"alt":147,"src":148},"Powershell","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FSc2Y8ab.png",[16,150,151,152,155,156,159,160,163],{},"如果不確定是否已經更改成功，可以進去 ",[80,153,154],{},"C:\\Python27\\Scripts"," 找看看 ",[80,157,158],{},"autosub.py"," 是否已經更改成 ",[80,161,162],{},"autosub_app.py","。",[16,165,166,167,170],{},"4.將剛剛下載的 ffmpeg 解壓縮，然後找到裡面的 ",[80,168,169],{},"ffmpeg.exe"," 複製起來",[16,172,173],{},"(路徑: ffmpeg-4.1.3-win64-static\\bin)",[16,175,176],{},[65,177],{"alt":178,"src":179},"ffmpeg","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FeycQA95.png",[16,181,182],{},"接下來貼到 Python 目錄下",[16,184,185],{},[65,186],{"alt":178,"src":187},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FiYFAa4V.png",[12,189,191],{"id":190},"調整-autosub-程式碼","調整 autosub 程式碼",[16,193,194,195,197],{},"接下來必須調整 ",[80,196,162],{}," 內部程式碼否則無法正常運作。",[16,199,200,201,204,205],{},"將約 48 行 ",[80,202,203],{},"temp = tempfile.NamedTemporaryFile(suffix='.flac')"," 修改為 ",[80,206,207],{},"temp = tempfile.NamedTemporaryFile(suffix='.flac', delete=False)",[16,209,210],{},[65,211],{"alt":212,"src":213},"autosub_app","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FtA8Wkgo.png",[16,215,216],{},"最後還有一個雷點一定要調整，否則絕對無法編譯，要將 138 ~ 140 的程式碼註解掉",[16,218,219],{},[65,220],{"alt":221,"src":222},"很重要","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002F8GYdlLE.png",[12,224,226],{"id":225},"ai-自動替影片產生字幕","AI 自動替影片產生字幕",[16,228,229],{},"終於到最後一步驟，接下來試著在指令視窗下輸入以下指令",[73,231,233],{"className":75,"code":232,"language":77,"meta":78,"style":78},"C:\\Python27\\python.exe C:\\Python27\\scripts\\autosub_app.py --list-languages\n",[80,234,235],{"__ignoreMap":78},[83,236,237],{"class":85,"line":86},[83,238,232],{},[16,240,241],{},[65,242],{"alt":243,"src":244},"python","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FdfsAmrj.png",[16,246,247],{},"這些代表著可辨識的語言及辨識後生成的語言字幕，這邊只需要記得 zh-TW 即可。",[16,249,250],{},[65,251],{"alt":243,"src":252},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FZUqp9Vx.png",[16,254,255],{},"接下來只需要輸入以下指令就可以自動辨識及生成字幕啦~",[73,257,259],{"className":75,"code":258,"language":77,"meta":78,"style":78},"C:\\Python27\\python.exe C:\\Python27\\scripts\\autosub_app.py -S zh-TW -D zh-TW Video.mp4\n",[80,260,261],{"__ignoreMap":78},[83,262,263],{"class":85,"line":86},[83,264,258],{},[16,266,267],{},"指令說明:",[73,269,271],{"className":75,"code":270,"language":77,"meta":78,"style":78},"C:\\Python27\\python.exe C:\\Python27\\scripts\\autosub_app.py -S 辨識語言 -D 輸出語言 影片路徑\n",[80,272,273],{"__ignoreMap":78},[83,274,275],{"class":85,"line":86},[83,276,270],{},[16,278,279],{},"以我的影片路徑做範例的話，就像這樣",[73,281,283],{"className":75,"code":282,"language":77,"meta":78,"style":78},"C:\\Python27\\python.exe C:\\Python27\\scripts\\autosub_app.py -S zh-TW -D zh-TW C:\\Users\\Hsiangfeng\\Downloads\\Veido\\test.mp4\n",[80,284,285],{"__ignoreMap":78},[83,286,287],{"class":85,"line":86},[83,288,282],{},[16,290,291],{},"編譯速度非常快，所以一下子就生成好哩",[16,293,294],{},[65,295],{"alt":296,"src":297},"AI 自動生成字幕","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002F6Y3nCD9.png",[12,299,300],{"id":300},"參考文獻",[16,302,303],{},[36,304,307],{"href":305,"rel":306},"https:\u002F\u002Fmoon-half.info\u002Fp\u002F2993",[40],"影片自動產生字幕",[16,309,310],{},[36,311,314],{"href":312,"rel":313},"https:\u002F\u002Fgithub.com\u002Fagermanidis\u002Fautosub\u002Fissues\u002F31",[40],"Install AutoSub Step to Step in Windows with Translate subtitle",[316,317,318],"style",{},"html .default .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}",{"title":78,"searchDepth":320,"depth":320,"links":321},2,[322,323,324,325,326,327],{"id":14,"depth":320,"text":14},{"id":24,"depth":320,"text":24},{"id":58,"depth":320,"text":58},{"id":190,"depth":320,"text":191},{"id":225,"depth":320,"text":226},{"id":300,"depth":320,"text":300},"2019-05-31 10:44:35","md","zh-Hant",{},true,"\u002Fpython\u002Fpython-srt","2",{"title":6,"description":18},false,"Python\u002F使用-Python-替影片自動產生字幕-srt-檔",[67,339,340],"AI","字幕",null,"\u002Fpython\u002F20190531\u002F407